Regarding the control instructions for the exe executable files in this project;

In olcEngine3D part3.exe and part4.exe;
1. Press W/S button for move forward/backward.
2. Press A/D button for controlling camera to rotate to left/right.
3. Press Up/Down button for move towards top/button in the world.
4. Press Left/Right button for strafe Left/Right.(but it's inverse in part4.exe.just a bug)

Note:
There is no control context in olcEngine3D part1 and part2.